      <title>香港对市场操纵者判处创纪录监禁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/hk-court-hands-out-longest-jail-time-for-market-manipulation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据主审法官称，香港法院以市场操纵罪判处两名被告六年零八个月监禁，这是香港迄今为止对此类罪行判处的最长刑期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/hk-court-hands-out-longest-jail-time-for-market-manipulation</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 04:32:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
